Package se.jguru.nazgul.core.quickstart.api.generator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ComponentFactory
    Specification for how to create a new Software Component, which consists of several collaborating Maven projects within the same reactor.
    ProjectFactory
    Specification for how to generate a new project structure in an empty or non-existent directory.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractComponentFactory
    Abstract ComponentFactory implementation sporting utility methods and VCS/Project navigation facilities.
    AbstractFactory
    Abstract utility implementations for all Factory classes, including POM synthesis and naming validation.
    AbstractProjectFactory
    Abstract implementation of the ProjectFactory sporting
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SoftwareComponentPart
    Definition of all known SoftwareComponent parts, implying the different Maven projects which together create a SoftwareComponent.
